node.text:
FaceTiming shoot with @paolatambunann !!!!! Shooting in face time can be pretty hard because the phone might not focus properly and you can’t tap to focus. But it certainly trains one to direct their model or friends easier. And also your friends will probably know how to shoot by themselves with a tripod afterwards 😂

Photos are taken via FaceTiming live shoot 
#facetimephotoshoot #stayhomephotochallenge #quarantinephotography #stayhomesg #stayhomestaysafe #creativephotography
